(5, 'C√°ch √în Thi ƒê·∫°i H·ªçc Hi·ªáu Qu·∫£ (27 ƒêi·ªÉm Trong 3 Th√°ng)', '<div>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-1704ce82133\"><strong>TRONG 3 TH&Aacute;NG &Ocirc;N THI ƒê·∫†T 27 ƒêI·ªÇM?</strong><br /><strong>TH·∫¨T HAY ƒê&Ugrave;A?</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16a2b4aa0fa\">B·∫°n c&oacute; bi·∫øt r·∫±ng hi·ªán nay, h·ªá th·ªëng Gi&aacute;o d·ª•c c·ªßa ch&uacute;ng ta thay ƒë·ªïi v&agrave; c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t li&ecirc;n t·ª•c h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng? Th·∫≠m ch&iacute; l&agrave; t·ª´ng gi&acirc;y...</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16a2b4aa0fb\">ƒê&atilde; bao gi·ªù b·∫°n t·ª± h·ªèi r·∫±ng: &ldquo;<em>L&agrave;m th·∫ø n&agrave;o ƒë·ªÉ h·ªçc gi·ªèi h∆°n khi n·ªÅn gi&aacute;o d·ª•c m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng ta ƒëang s·ªëng n&oacute; thay ƒë·ªïi nhi·ªÅu nh∆∞ v·∫≠y?</em>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-css=\"tve-u-1704cf181ff\"><img style=\"height: auto; width: 724px;\" title=\"33548c5e7de2b46d0f43f46c4f1141d7-1450172811569\" src=\"https://tuhoc365.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/33548c5e7de2b46d0f43f46c4f1141d7-1450172811569.gif\" alt=\"B·∫ø t·∫Øc\" width=\"500\" height=\"216\" data-id=\"78302\" data-css=\"tve-u-1704cf1820a\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16a2b4aa0fc\"><strong>C&oacute; ph·∫£i b·∫°n ƒëang b·∫ø t·∫Øc</strong>&nbsp;v&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng bi·∫øt ph∆∞∆°ng ph&aacute;p, chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c &ocirc;n thi ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc hi·ªáu qu·∫£ nh·∫•t kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16a2b4aa0fe\"><em>C&oacute; th·ªÉ b·∫°n ƒë&atilde; nghe h&agrave;ng tri·ªáu &yacute; ki·∫øn kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave; m·ªôt v&agrave;i l·ªùi khuy&ecirc;n l&agrave;m b·∫°n tr·ªü n&ecirc;n r·ªëi h∆°n bao gi·ªù h·∫øt&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16a2b4aa0fe\"><strong>C&oacute; ph·∫£i b·∫°n ƒëang hoang mang v&agrave; khao kh&aacute;t</strong>&nbsp;t&igrave;m ƒë∆∞·ª£c h∆∞·ªõng ƒëi ƒë&uacute;ng ƒë·∫Øn ƒë·ªÉ tƒÉng nhanh ƒëi·ªÉm s·ªë trong th·ªùi gian ng·∫Øn.</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16a2b4aa0ff\">V·∫≠y th&igrave; b·∫°n ƒë&atilde; ·ªü ƒë&uacut