h&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kh·∫£ nƒÉng ƒë·∫≠u ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc hu·ªëng chi l&agrave; ƒë·∫≠u v&agrave;o nh·ªØng tr∆∞·ªùng Top nh∆∞ t&ocirc;i mong mu·ªën.</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a425\">B·∫°n bi·∫øt kh&ocirc;ng, h·ªìi ·∫•y th&iacute;ch l·∫Øm c∆°, t&ocirc;i r·∫•t th&iacute;ch ƒë·∫øn tr∆∞·ªùng. ƒê·ªÉ l&agrave;m g&igrave; ∆∞? C&oacute; ph·∫£i l&agrave;m &ldquo;con ngoan tr&ograve; gi·ªèi kh&ocirc;ng&rdquo; üòâ ?</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a426\">T&ocirc;i th&iacute;ch ƒë·∫øn tr∆∞·ªùng ch·ªâ v&igrave; ng·∫Øm crush, ƒë∆∞·ª£c tr&ograve; chuy·ªán c&ugrave;ng crush&hellip; c·∫£ ng&ocirc;i tr∆∞·ªùng v&agrave; t∆∞∆°ng lai thu b&eacute; l·∫°i v·ª´a b·∫±ng crush.</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a428\">H·ªìi ·∫•y t&ocirc;i ng&acirc;y th∆° l·∫Øm, t&ocirc;i mu·ªën c·∫£ th·∫ø gi·ªõi n&agrave;y v&igrave; t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u m&atilde;nh li·ªát c·ªßa t&ocirc;i m&agrave; thay ƒë·ªïi m·ªôt ch&uacute;t&hellip; nh∆∞ng gi·∫•c m∆° ch·ªâ m&atilde;i l&agrave; m·ªông t∆∞·ªüng, t&ocirc;i ph·∫£i tr·ªü l·∫°i v·ªõi th·ª±c t·∫ø ngay khi ch·ªâ c&ograve;n 3 th&aacute;ng cu·ªëi.</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a429\">T&ocirc;i d·ª± t&iacute;nh t&iacute;nh thi kh·ªëi A - To&aacute;n L&yacute; H&oacute;a. V&igrave; crush, v&igrave; m·∫£i ham ch∆°i v·ªõi l≈© b·∫°n n&ecirc;n ƒëi·ªÉm s·ªë d·∫≠m ch&acirc;n t·∫°i ch·ªó m·ªôt th·ªùi gian.. sau ƒë&oacute; th·∫£ d·ªëc kh&ocirc;ng phanh. Th·ªùi ƒëi·ªÉm t·ªìi t·ªá l&agrave; c&aacute;i ng&agrave;y t&ocirc;i b·ªã m·ªùi ph·ª• huynh &ldquo;ch·ªâ v&igrave;&rdquo; ƒë·ªôi s·ªï l·ªõp chuy&ecirc;n l&yacute;.</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a42a\">C&oacute; ph·∫£i ph·ª• huynh b·ªã x·∫•u h·ªï l&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tuhoc365.vn/3-buoc-tu-hoc-on-thi-dai-hoc-o-nha-van-thanh-thu-khoa/\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline;\">ƒë·ªông l·ª±c ƒë·ªÉ t&ocirc;i thay ƒë·ªïi kh&ocirc;ng?</span></a></p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a42b\">C&oacute; th·ªÉ n&oacute; ƒë&uacute;ng v·ªõi b·∫°n, nh∆∞ng v·ªõi t&ocirc;i th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a42c\">B·∫°n c&oacute; ƒëang t&ograve; m&ograve; t·ª± h·ªèi t·∫°i sao t&ocirc;i quy·∫øt t&acirc;m ƒë·∫≠u ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc&hellip; ƒë·ªÉ r·ªìi t·ª´ cu·ªëi l·ªõp tr·ªü th&agrave;nh TOP ƒë·∫ßu c·ªßa ng&ocirc;i tr∆∞·ªùng? V&agrave; ƒë&ocirc;i khi ch·ªâ c·∫ßn b·∫°n bi·∫øt ƒë∆∞·ª£c l&yacute; do, b·∫°n c&oacute; th·ªÉ B·ª®C PH&Aacute; ƒëi·ªÉm s·ªë nhanh ch&oacute;ng trong th·ªùi gian ng·∫Øn t·ªõi?</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a42d\">Ng&agrave;y t&ocirc;i b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu cu·ªôc h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh chinh ph·ª•c c&aacute;nh c·ª≠a ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc, t&ocirc;i tr&agrave;n ƒë·∫ßy &yacute; ch&iacute;, ƒë·ªông l·ª±c v&agrave; quy·∫øt t&acirc;m&hellip; nh∆∞ b·∫°n b&acirc;y gi·ªù v·∫≠y.</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a42e\">Ng&agrave;y ·∫•y l&agrave; m·ªôt ng&agrave;y ƒë·∫ßy ƒëau bu·ªìn&hellip; b·∫°n c&oacute; hi·ªÉu ƒë∆∞·ª£c c·∫£m gi&aacute;c ng∆∞·ªùi m&igrave;nh th∆∞∆°ng, th∆∞∆°ng ng∆∞·ªùi kh&aacute;c hay kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a42f\">T&ocirc;i ƒë&atilde; t·ª± giam m&igrave;nh trong cƒÉn ph&ograve;ng nh·ªè, kh&oacute;a tr&aacute;i c·ª≠a, v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ƒÉn g&igrave;&hellip;</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a431\">T&ocirc;i ƒë&atilde; g&agrave;o l&ecirc;n v·ªõi 4 b·ª©c t∆∞·ªùng nh∆∞ m·ªôt ng∆∞·ªùi ƒëi&ecirc;n&hellip; &ldquo;Th·∫±ng ƒë&oacute; th&igrave; c&oacute; g&igrave; h∆°n tao&hellip; t·∫°i sao em l·∫°i theo n&oacute;!&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16aeef0a432\">T&ocirc;i d·∫ßn t·ªânh t&aacute;o, v&agrave; nh&igrave;n nh·∫≠n l·∫°i m·ªôt c&aacute;ch r&otilde; r&agrave;ng&hellip; n&oacute; c&oacute; g&igrave; h∆°n t&ocirc;i ch·ª©? Uhm&hellip; th&igrave;.. ƒë·∫πp trai h∆°n, bi·∫øt ch∆°i ·∫£o thu·∫≠t, h&aacute;t rap hay, ƒë&agrave;n piano gi·ªèi, rich kid&hellip;. nh∆∞ng ƒëi·ªÅu quan tr·ªçng h∆°n h·∫øt n&oacute; thi th·ª≠ ƒë∆∞·ª£c 27 ƒëi·ªÉm&hellip; c&ograve;n t&ocirc;i ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ª£c 17 ƒëi·ªÉm...</p>\r\n<p data-css=\"tve-u-16ae