(6, '√în thi THPT qu·ªëc gia theo chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c n√†o?', '<p>ƒê·ªÉ ƒë·∫°t hi·ªáu qu·∫£ cao trong k·ª≥ thi THPT qu·ªëc gia c·∫ßn c&oacute; chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c h·ªçc t·∫≠p ph&ugrave; h·ª£p. Sau ƒë&acirc;y l&agrave; 4 giai ƒëo·∫°n quan tr·ªçng m&agrave; m·ªói h·ªçc sinh n&ecirc;n x&acirc;y d·ª±ng.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>Kh·ªüi ƒë·ªông - n·∫Øm ch·∫Øc ki·∫øn th·ª©c s&aacute;ch gi&aacute;o khoa<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>M·ªói h·ªçc sinh n&ecirc;n ghi nh·ªõ &ldquo;S&aacute;ch gi&aacute;o khoa lu&ocirc;n ƒë&uacute;ng&rdquo;, hay &iacute;t nh·∫•t n·ªôi dung trong ƒë·ªÅ thi c·ªßa B·ªô GD&amp;ƒêT ƒë·ªÅu n·∫±m trong s&aacute;ch gi&aacute;o khoa. V&igrave; v·∫≠y, tr∆∞·ªõc khi b∆∞·ªõc v&agrave;o cu·ªôc ƒëua ƒë·∫øn c&aacute;c tr∆∞·ªùng ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc, cao ƒë·∫≥ng, b·∫°n ph·∫£i c&oacute; b∆∞·ªõc kh·ªüi ƒë·ªông k·ªπ, &ocirc;n l·∫°i ki·∫øn th·ª©c l·ªõp 10, 11 ƒë·ªìng th·ªùi h·ªçc v&agrave; n·∫Øm ƒë∆∞·ª£c c&aacute;c ki·∫øn th·ª©c c∆° b·∫£n l·ªõp 12.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c b·∫°n kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n qu&aacute; h·∫•p t·∫•p, v·ªôi v&agrave;ng, ƒë·ªët ch&aacute;y giai ƒëo·∫°n b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu &ocirc;n thi ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc lu&ocirc;n. Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y, b·∫°n s·∫Ω r·∫•t d·ªÖ n·∫£n v&igrave; c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c ph·∫£i nh·∫≠n m·ªôt l∆∞·ª£ng ki·∫øn th·ª©c qu&aacute; l·ªõn, m·∫•t ph∆∞∆°ng h∆∞·ªõng v&agrave; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh luy·ªán thi ƒë·∫°i h·ªçc s·∫Ω kh&ocirc;ng hi·ªáu qu·∫£.</p>\r\n<table style=\"width: 660px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><img style=\"height: auto; width: 660px;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://znews-photo.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/Ycgmvlbp/2015_04_22/chien_luoc_on_thi_1.jpg\" alt=\"Chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c &ocirc;ng thi qua h&igrave;nh v·∫Ω.\" data-title=\"null\" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c &ocirc;n thi qua h&igrave;nh v·∫Ω.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Ch·∫°y b·ªÅn - trang b·ªã ki·∫øn th·ª©c &ocirc;n thi THPT qu·ªëc gia</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sau khi kh·ªüi ƒë·ªông, b·∫°n ƒë&atilde; n·∫Øm ƒë∆∞·ª£c c&aacute;c ki·∫øn th·ª