rong c·∫•u tr&uacute;c ƒë·ªÅ thi THPT qu·ªëc gia.</p>\r\n<p>Nh·ªØng b·∫°n h·ªçc l·ª±c kh&aacute;, c·∫ßn r&agrave; so&aacute;t, &ocirc;n t·∫≠p l·∫°i ph·∫ßn l&yacute; thuy·∫øt, ki·∫øn th·ª©c cƒÉn b·∫£n. B&ecirc;n c·∫°nh ƒë&oacute;, n·∫Øm ƒë∆∞·ª£c c&aacute;c ph∆∞∆°ng ph&aacute;p gi·∫£i b&agrave;i t·∫≠p kh&oacute; v&agrave; l∆∞u &yacute; tr&aacute;nh m·∫•t ƒëi·ªÉm ·ªü b&agrave;i t·∫≠p d·ªÖ, trung b&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, ƒë·ªÉ l&agrave;m ƒë∆∞·ª£c c&aacute;c c&acirc;u h·ªèi thu·ªôc m·ª©c ƒë·ªô v·∫≠n d·ª•ng cao, b·∫°n c·∫ßn ph·∫£i n·∫Øm th·∫≠t ch·∫Øc ki·∫øn th·ª©c cƒÉn b·∫£n.</p>\r\n<p>Nh·ªØng th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·∫ßy c&ocirc; t·∫°i trung t&acirc;m&nbsp;<em>H·ªçc m&atilde;i</em>&nbsp;ƒë&uacute;c r&uacute;t kinh nghi·ªám.</p>\r\n</div>', 'https://znews-photo.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/Ycgmvlbp/2015_04_22/chien_luoc_on_thi_1.jpg', '2020-07-10 09:58:55', '2020-07-10 09:58:55', 12);

